## Purpose
Return logged-in user profile from JWT.

## Response 200
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "data": { "id", "email", "full_name", "client_org_id", "role", "created_at" }
}
```
401 UNAUTHORIZED · 401 SESSION_INVALID

## Purpose
List PDFs uploaded for this org (metadata + paths).

## Response 200
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "data": {
    "documents": [
      { "id", "client_org_id", "filename", "document_path", "document_type", "processing_status", "created_at" }
    ]
  }
}
```
404 CLIENT_ORG_NOT_FOUND

